text: St Andrew's Catholic College, is a Catholic co-educational P-12 school in Cairns, Queensland, Australia. St Andrew's is located in the Redlynch Valley, Cairns and is part of the Northern Beaches Parish of Holy Cross. ==See also== * List of schools in Far North Queensland * Catholic education in Australia ==References== ==External links== * St Andrew's Catholic College Website * Category:Schools in Cairns Category:Catholic secondary schools in Queensland Category:Catholic primary schools in Queensland Category:Educational institutions established in 2001 Category:2001 establishments in Australia
